<li><i><a href="http://www.lastnamehistory.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.lastnamehistory.com/" rel="nofollow">LastName History Multi Search</a></i></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFNeil_Summers2006">Neil Summers (2006-11-04). <a href="http://www.amlwchhistory.co.uk/data/welshsurnamemeanings.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.amlwchhistory.co.uk/data/welshsurnamemeanings.htm" rel="nofollow">"Welsh surnames and their meaning"</a>. <i>Amlwch history databases</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.amlwchhistory.co.uk/data/welshsurnamemeanings.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.amlwchhistory.co.uk/data/welshsurnamemeanings.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.amlwchhistory.co.uk/data/welshsurnamemeanings.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-09-19</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Welsh+surnames+and+their+meaning&amp;rft.atitle=Amlwch+history+databases&amp;rft.aulast=Neil+Summers&amp;rft.au=Neil+Summers&amp;rft.date=2006-11-04&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amlwchhistory.co.uk%2Fdata%2Fwelshsurnamemeanings.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Family_name"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
